  <summary date="2015-02-27T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Distillery Excise Tax Reform Act of 2015

Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow a reduction (from $13.50 to $2.70 on each proof gallon produced in the United States) in the excise tax on distilled spirits for domestic distillers who produce not more than 100,000 proof gallons of distilled spirits during the calendar year.</summary>
